&lt;p&gt;work fine in the version of Validator in SVN.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;abc@abc_def.com&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;fails validation, as underscore is not allowed in host names.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13021399" author="wglass" created="Tue, 19 Apr 2011 04:04:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry.  Typo!  I&apos;ve tried abc@abc-def.com and it correctly works.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll try trunk and see if that helps.  I&apos;m using the @Email tag with spring-modules-validation.  Maybe that affects this in some manner.  I&apos;ll report back.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
